      <div class="time"><span id="s">0</span><small>Seconds</small></div>
    </section>

    <!--<a class="cta" href="#about">Enter the Quest</a>-->
  </header>
</main>




<section class="about" id="about">
  <div class="wrap">
    <h2>About Moroni's Quest</h2>
    <p>Moroni’s Quest is an immersive youth camp engaging participants in the stories of the Book of Mormon through theatrical experiences, teamwork, and discipleship.</p>
<section class="mq-about-banners">

  <article class="mq-banner" style="--bg:url('/img/banner_live.webp')">
    <div class="mq-banner__content">
      <h3><span class="accent-story">LIVE</span> THE STORY</h3>
      <p>
        Walk where heroes once stood—relive the faith, courage, and miracles of the scriptures.
      </p>
    </div>
  </article>

  <div class="mq-banner-divider">
    <span></span>
    <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
      <path d="M12 2l8 4v6c0 5-3.4 9.4-8 10-4.6-.6-8-5-8-10V6l8-4z"/>
    </svg>
    <span></span>
  </div>

  <article class="mq-banner" style="--bg:url('/img/banner_embrace.webp')">
    <div class="mq-banner__content">
      <h3><span class="accent-story">EMBRACE</span> YOUR FAMILY</h3>
      <p>
        Every quest starts with a family—serve, laugh, and overcome challenges together.
      </p>
    </div>
  </article>

  <div class="mq-banner-divider">
    <span></span>
    <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
      <path d="M12 2l8 4v6c0 5-3.4 9.4-8 10-4.6-.6-8-5-8-10V6l8-4z"/>
    </svg>
    <span></span>
  </div>

  <article class="mq-banner" style="--bg:url('/img/banner_deepen.webp')">
    <div class="mq-banner__content">
      <h3><span class="accent-story">DEEPEN</span> YOUR FAITH</h3>
      <p>
        As you relive the stories, find the Savior’s hand in your own.
      </p>
    </div>
  </article>

</section>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="camp-details">

  <div class="wrap">

    <div class="camp-header">
      <img
        src="/img/TannerCampLogo.png"
        alt="Tanner Youth Camp logo"
        class="camp-logo"
      />
      <div>
        <h2>Tanner Youth Camp</h2>
        <p class="camp-tagline">
          Home of Moroni’s Quest for the Sherwood Park Stake.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="camp-grid">

      <!-- Location + Map -->
      <article class="camp-card">
        <h3>Where</h3>
        <p class="camp-location">
          <span class="pin">📍</span>
          Tanner Youth Camp<br />
          5007 Lakeshore Rd<br />
          Wabamun, AB T0E 2K0
        </p>



        <div class="map-wrap">
          <div class="mapouter">
            <div class="gmap_canvas">
              <iframe class="gmap_iframe" width="100%" frameborder="0" scrolling="no" marginheight="0" marginwidth="0" src="https://maps.google.com/maps?width=600&amp;height=400&amp;hl=en&amp;q=5007 Lakeshore Rd, Wabamun, AB T0E 2K0&amp;t=&amp;z=14&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;iwloc=B&amp;output=embed"></iframe>
              <a href="https://embed-googlemap.com">embed-googlemap.com</a>
            </div>
            <style>.mapouter{position:relative;text-align:right;width:100%;height:400px;}.gmap_canvas {overflow:hidden;background:none!important;width:100%;height:400px;}.gmap_iframe {height:400px!important;}
            </style>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="map-note">When you arrive look for the designated drop-off area.</p>
      </article>

      <!-- When / Cost / Eligibility -->
      <article class="camp-card">
        <h3>When &amp; Who</h3>
        <ul class="camp-list">
          <li><strong>Dates:</strong> July 7–10, 2026</li>
         <li><strong>Leader Check-in:</strong> July 7 at 7:30 AM (previous-night check-in available)</li>
          <li><strong>Youth Check-in:</strong> July 7 at 9:00 AM </li>
          <li><strong>Cost:</strong> No cost for youth of the stake.</li>
        </ul>
        <h4>Eligibility</h4>
        <p>Youth turning 14 in 2026 up to those graduating Grade 12 in 2026.</p>
        <h4>Conduct</h4>
        <p>All activities follow Church standards. We invite every youth to come ready to have fun, be kind, and help keep the Spirit of the camp.</p>
        <img src="/img/youth3.jpg" alt="Youth at camp" class="camp-card-img"/>
      </article>

      <!-- Program Outline -->
      <article class="camp-card">
        <h3>What to Expect</h3>
        <p>
          Moroni’s Quest lets youth taste what it might have been like to live
          in Book of Mormon times.
        </p>
        <ul class="camp-list">
          <li>Scripture-based reenactments and dramatizations</li>
          <li>Tribe activities, challenges, and games</li>
          <li>Discussions and Devotionals</li>
        </ul>
        <p>During the day, youth are placed in tribes to experience stories, battles, and lessons from the Book of Mormon. </p>
        <p>In the evenings, tribes remain together for activities and camping. Male and female youth sleep in separate tents, with leaders sleeping in separate tents within the same camping area.</p>
        <p>
          Our goal is simple: build faith in Jesus Christ, deepen love for the
          Book of Mormon, and create memories you’ll never forget.
        </p>
      </article>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

